{"tid":1908750,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"麥當勞啲辣醬真係好貴","createTime":"2020-03-03T13:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T10:43:53.000Z","uid":195123,"like":14,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"36cbd1ba3fc2179b4fa5881a735c761cc9b3c594","tid":1908750,"uid":195123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:20:42.000Z","msg":"阿叔我今日幫襯麥當勞 叫左一盒雞翼<br />\n竟然比得一包辣醬我 得一包辣醬叫我點樣去食4隻雞翼啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過唔驚！好在我成身紋身大大隻！於是我就去同取餐位個𡃁妹R一包辣醬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n  我：喂 比多包醬我啦 <br />\n𡃁妹：辣醬一蚊一包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n  （我心諗唔通我個樣唔夠樣衰？啲紋身唔夠嚇人？唔得！我要比啲掙扎！）<br />\n<br />\n  我：我想要多一包辣醬 4隻雞翼wor!我開2件都比一包啦！一盒4件都一包？！<br />\n𡃁妹：係啊 無論一盒定一袋雞翼 都淨跟一包辣醬 額外要就一蚊一包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我戈下真係好嬲！我忍唔住吶喊出我嘅心聲！<br />\n：我都係想要多一包泰式辣醬啫！！要一蚊？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後原本係後面做緊其他野嘅店員 好似感受到我對辣醬嘅一份執着 於是有另一個女仔行咗過嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁我諗住佢會比多一包我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知！佢比返22蚊我！仲拎走左我盒雞翼！<br />\n個女仔同我講：依度退返一盒雞翼嘅錢比你 你可以重新落過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我都係想要多一包醬啫！點解要一蚊！一蚊咁貴！我乞足一日食先搵到個唔知幾多個一蚊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔得！我好嬲！我要報復！<br />\n於是機智又聰明嘅我 拎咗一杯價值12.5蚊嘅奶昔 淋尻佢地門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係大快人心"},{"pid":"5540ff32a372a4848d229b2688c9d393758703f9","tid":1908750,"uid":9193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:22:06.000Z","msg":"thx for share"},{"pid":"1ca070ea1e2eb93070be2490bc855a620354d14a","tid":1908750,"uid":72457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:22:23.000Z","msg":"要醬比多蚊"},{"pid":"2c4ad0806ca47bfe34f3fdc9db92048817b17783","tid":1908750,"uid":175969,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:23:25.000Z","msg":"夠鐘食藥了"},{"pid":"b516c6bd26f02394206703ae5adec3302a179ba8","tid":1908750,"uid":29204,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:23:33.000Z","msg":"仲食麥當勞屌你老母"},{"pid":"2a066aed04ea18f4b0fab2fed2fd76e70817c796","tid":1908750,"uid":55279,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:24:54.000Z","msg":"喺香港食就屌你老母"},{"pid":"68d634eb961d6c74106ae80b3b073af289777bd3","tid":1908750,"uid":36443,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:25:49.000Z","msg":"專登入嚟屌樓主食金拱門嘅你可以正評呢個回覆<br />\n然後返上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔使推post㗎啦"},{"pid":"0a2621efe69bc8ce10bee959cb64f4999c94a480","tid":1908750,"uid":177620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:26:38.000Z","msg":"分開買兩包<br />\nsor太認真"},{"pid":"2d5f3fe1ddace0c2e4ec2782db957e0d69161607","tid":1908750,"uid":195123,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:49:05.000Z","msg":"阿叔我紋曬身黑鼆鼆幫襯元朗圍村附近嘅麥當勞大家知我咩料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw有冇人想睇我嘅英姿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f412c8485875c68f53a16c4760f23a878d30b13a","tid":1908750,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:51:31.000Z","msg":"喺個口度！"},{"pid":"a5c5ce1ebe1e2b8c6d8a041bbbc8bb486da66709","tid":1908750,"uid":40766,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:52:10.000Z","msg":"屌你老母仲食麥當勞。"},{"pid":"fb9b73c88a5018ca1da538cb9616d61bc68b68e3","tid":1908750,"uid":54126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:59:06.000Z","msg":"負皮 上一頁"},{"pid":"b8dcfad7c00fc22c5dd6adbc6b62af04f50c86ef","tid":1908750,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:54:00.000Z","msg":"red"},{"pid":"b0fc7d8c72ed80cfa4fd9613db47995de3b76401","tid":1908750,"uid":214475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T18:29:39.000Z","msg":"而家每次都係分開 2隻2隻咁買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfff8c2c3d8d70f9eddbac482d88615a4eca8124","tid":1908750,"uid":34500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T10:36:27.000Z","msg":"點解唔淋個職員牙？<br />\n你都唔夠霸氣"},{"pid":"2bc06af263bef39de02ad8f00a584a6fd1317d3a","tid":1908750,"uid":127233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T10:43:53.000Z","msg":"樓主大陸西,無錢學人食野"}]}